headline: Be a Nuclear Family! D.C. Households May Choose Clean Nuclear Energy with America’s First-Ever Nuclear-Powered Consumer Energy Plan from Constellation
summary: BALTIMORE, December 17, 2024--Constellation announced the first-ever U.S. product allowing consumers to power their homes with 100% nuclear energy, through a new pilot program.
